<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"><br/>

<span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>If you've applied to adopt a cat, you do not need to read or reply to this email.</strong></span><br/>
<span style="font-size: 14px;"> Congratulations on your decision to add a rescue dog to your family! We know that you and your family are hoping to gain a new best friend so we have some guides for you to review before making the final commitment. This information is important to ensure the safety of your children, children in the community, and a potential adopted dog. Moving into a new home is a bit stressful for any dog, regardless of how secure of an environment you are providing for them. It is crucial that you talk with all family members about these points before bringing a new dog into your household.</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"> </p>
<ul>
<li style="line-height: 1.2; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">77% of all dog bites occur in children and are from a family or friend’s dog, but following appropriate safety measures can significantly reduce this risk. <a href="https://www.thefamilydog.com/stop-the-77/" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Watch this video to understand the 77%</a></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"> </p>
<ul>
<li style="line-height: 1.2; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Many rescue dogs have never lived with a family in a home before, and may have never interacted with children very much, it is imperative to take things slow while the dog is getting to know your rules and children</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"> </p>
<ul>
<li style="line-height: 1.2; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Be prepared to keep the dog in a crate during any times when you cannot supervise them directly with your children</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"> </p>
<ul>
<li style="line-height: 1.2; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Before making the final decision, please review the appropriate resources below with your children or children that you regularly interact with. It is important to talk about what their behavior Should look like around your new furry friend.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"> </p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; mso-line-height-alt: 19px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Please Watch These Fun Videos with your Children. </strong></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"> </span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>For Everyone</strong></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video-  <a href="https://youtu.be/VPEwHhXF6pU" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Pat, Pet, Pause</a> </span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/8AaNg1rMjak" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">How to Kiss a Dog</a></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/HqlFuQfL8Lo" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Strange Dog, Play it Safe</a></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/YI1EBub2mgI" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Child/ Dog Interactions</a>, This is More of a Parent's Guide</span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"> </span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/FXdgNqB0xNg" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Dog Bite Safety with Jimmy the Dog</a></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"> </span></p>
<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px; mso-line-height-alt: 17px; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Video- <a href="https://www.gooddoginabox.com/meet-new-dog/" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">How to Meet a New Dog</a></span></p>
