<p style="line-height: 1.2; word-break: break-word; mso-line-height-alt: NaNpx; margin: 0;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> <strong>For Babies &amp; Infants</strong></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Article- <a href="https://www.doggonesafe.com/baby_safety_around_dogs" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Baby's Safety Around Dogs </a></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Article- <a href="https://www.akc.org/expert-advice/training/how-to-introduce-babies-and-dogs/" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Helpful Hints When Introducing Babies and Dogs</a></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Article- <a href="https://drsophiayin.com/blog/entry/keeping_dogs_kids_and_infants_safe_in_the_same_household/" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Dogs and Babies: Can They be Safe in the Same Household?</a></span><br/> <br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> <strong>For Preschoolers</strong></span><br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/36Z9RRjiQMA" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">I Speak Doggy</a></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> <strong>For Elementary</strong></span><br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Video- <a href="https://youtu.be/MYDW2KV_TzE" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Dog Stars (Bite Prevention)</a></span><br/> <br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> <strong>For Older Kids</strong></span><br/><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Article- <a href="https://www.puppyleaks.com/teaching-dog-bite-prevention-kids/" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #0068A5;" target="_blank">Dog Bite prevention</a></span></p>
